Class SpdyHeaders

java.lang.Object
  org.jboss.netty.handler.codec.spdy.SpdyHeaders

public class SpdyHeaders
extends Object

Provides the constants for the standard SPDY HTTP header names and commonly used utility methods that access an SpdyHeaderBlock.
